title: Ep. - 334 - TIFFANY MOON FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF DALLAS RYAN AND KEVIN BERNARD FROM BURIED BY THE BERNARDS
description:
Tiffany Moon is the first medical doctor and first-generation Asian-American star of a Bravo franchise. The mother of two is the newest cast member of Real Housewives of Dallas. She talks to Kate about immigrating to the United States at six, beginning college at 17, her decision to join the show, and juggling career, home, and becoming a tv personality.

 

Ryan and Kevin Bernard and stars of Netflix’s new hilarious show Buried by the Bernards, about a family owned and operated funeral business in Memphis, Tennessee.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
